15:38.767 --> 15:40.433
Contacted him the next day.

15:40.500 --> 15:45.133
Don described the trailer as
a 16 foot black Terry trailer.

15:45.200 --> 15:50.000
So, unless the police officer was also,
again, psychotic,

15:50.066 --> 15:53.367
-you told him it was a 16 foot trailer.
-Mm-hmm.

15:53.433 --> 15:57.533
Did you not correct me before
and say it was a 20 foot trailer?

15:57.600 --> 15:58.967
I did correct you awhile ago.

15:59.033 --> 16:02.066
Well, you should've corrected
the police officer, too.

16:02.133 --> 16:04.400
No, he told you that it was not 20,

16:04.467 --> 16:06.333
-that it was 16.
-It was 16. Okay.

16:06.400 --> 16:08.834
-That's why I have her. Thank you.
