20:46.533 --> 20:49.700
from the little research that I had
time to do out on the bench,

20:49.767 --> 20:52.066
I know that he will not be
able to replace,

20:52.133 --> 20:56.000
or get a similar trailer to his own,
for the judgment that you made.

20:56.066 --> 20:58.667
And I think that he should have been
made whole with--

20:58.734 --> 21:02.033
Not a brand new trailer, but
at least the value of a used trailer

21:02.100 --> 21:04.900
that he could go and purchase and
then he would be made whole again.

