Does the fact that it was parked

21:17.300 --> 21:22.500
in somebody else's driveway, did that make
access easier for the criminal?

21:22.567 --> 21:27.300
Could have. I really believe that
what he paid for it 15 years ago

21:27.367 --> 21:33.200
was $1,500. He just put in the special
equipment and he said about $250.

21:33.266 --> 21:37.066
Well, then, I've at least made him
financially whole.

